<h2 class="article__header__heading">Putin Calls for International Settlements Based on Blockchain and Digital Currencies</h2>
<p>Russian President Vladimir Putin believes a new system for international money transfers is needed to reduce dependence on big banks and third parties. He is convinced that cross-border payments relying on digital currency and distributed ledger technology will be “much more convenient.”</p>
<p><a href="https://news.bitcoin.com/putin-calls-for-international-settlements-based-on-blockchain-and-digital-currencies/"><strong>Read More</strong></a></p>
